{"address1": "A-901-905, 215 Atrium", "address2": "9th Floor Andheri Kurla Road Andheri East", "city": "Mumbai", "zip": "400093", "country": "India", "phone": "91 22 6694 1800", "fax": "91 22 6694 1818", "website": "https://www.seamec.in", "industry": "Marine Shipping", "industryKey": "marine-shipping", "industryDisp": "Marine Shipping", "sector": "Industrials", "sectorKey": "industrials", "sectorDisp": "Industrials", "longBusinessSummary": "Seamec Limited provides offshore oilfield and diving support vessel services in India and internationally. The company's services include ROV operation support; inspection, maintenance, removal, and re-installation of single buoy moorings; pigging and retrieval of pigs; de burial and non-destructive testing of pipelines; location and arrest of gas leaks; replacement of caisson pipes and riser sections; installation and removal of risers; crossings and free span corrections; installation of riser clamps and anodes; flare booms repair; inspections and maintenance of PLEMs and pipelines; blowout control; installation of flexible pipeline; scanning and magnetic particle inspection of platform members; and assistance to jack-ups on well head maintenance. It also engages in charter and ship management and operation; operates shipping lines of freight and passenger transportation, as well as undertakes EPC tunnel projects, including road, railway, metro, soft ground, and water tunnels; and owns and operates bulk carriers. The company was formerly known as South East Asia Marine Engineering & Construction Limited and changed its name to Seamec Limited in June 2007. The company was incorporated in 1986 and is based in Mumbai, India. Seamec Limited is a subsidiary of HAL Offshore Limited.", "fullTimeEmployees": 68, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Vinay Kumar Agarwal", "title": "Chief Financial Officer", "fiscalYear": 2020, "totalPay": 4857413, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. K. T. Tho